==English==
===Etymology===
Old English [[elles#Old English|elles]] [[hwær]], corresponding to [[else]] + [[where]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/'ɛlswɛ:/}}

===Adverb===
'''elsewhere'''

# In or at some other place
#:''These particular trees are not to be found '''elsewhere'''.''
# To some other place
#:''If you won't serve us, we'll go '''elsewhere'''.''

